WEBVTT

NOTE bond hero film — dialogue and on-screen text

00:00:00.500 --> 00:00:04.500
[a low hum — two glass atoms joined by a luminous bond]

00:00:04.700 --> 00:00:09.400
[the camera dives inside the bond — threads of light rush past]

00:00:09.600 --> 00:00:14.000
[dawn. rey clocks in at his tailgate — a thread lifts from his phone]

00:00:14.300 --> 00:00:18.600
[macro: ty's thumb files a photo — the thread joins the weave]

00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:21.400
levvi: hi — it's levvi, with hale exteriors.

00:00:21.850 --> 00:00:22.850
levvi: your inspection passed.

00:00:23.200 --> 00:00:24.100
levvi: want the photos?

00:00:24.500 --> 00:00:28.100
[the threads fuse into a luminous lattice over the jobsite]

00:00:28.400 --> 00:00:33.000
[blue hour. marcus reads his phone: cedar ridge — on track — 8% under budget]

00:00:33.200 --> 00:00:36.700
[marcus smiles and pockets the phone]

00:00:37.500 --> 00:00:41.800
[on screen: AI-NATIVE CRM — WITH PROJECT INTELLIGENCE]
